The paper proposes a new asynchronous federated optimization algorithm for training on edge devices, which is a common problem in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also includes theoretical analysis of the algorithm's convergence properties, which could fall under the category of optimization and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of the algorithm for non-convex problems, which is a common area of research in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
